1.Name: The Curtain Falls
1.Desc:
<color=#FFFFFF>Active Skill</color>
Fire a series of random cards using a magic gun, each triggering different effects based on card type:
<color=#FFFFFF>Hearts</color> – Deals massive <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>.
<color=#FFFFFF>Spades</color> – Deals <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color> and inflicts massive Daze.
<color=#FFFFFF>Crowns</color> – Deals <color=#FE437E>Ether DMG</color> and accumulates massive <color=#FE437E>Ether Anomaly Buildup</color>.

1.Name: Master of Disguise
1.Desc:
<color=#FFFFFF>Additional Ability</color>
When there is at least 1 <color=#FFFFFF>Mockingbird</color> character in the squad: When the on-field Agent in the squad meets the Specialty requirements, the <color=#FFFFFF>Active Skill</color> fires a fixed card with a buff:
<color=#FFFFFF>Attack</color>: Fires only <color=#FFFFFF>Hearts</color>, increasing the DMG by 45%.
<color=#FFFFFF>Stun</color>: Fires only <color=#FFFFFF>Spades</color>, increasing the Daze buildup by 27%.
<color=#FFFFFF>Anomaly</color>: Fires only <color=#FFFFFF>Crowns</color>, increasing the Anomaly Buildup by 90%.
